'''Lehmstedt-Tanasescu反应'''（Lehmstedt-Tanasescu reaction）

通过用2-[[硝基|硝基]][[苯甲醛|苯甲醛]] (1)与[[芳香族化合物|芳香族化合物]] (2)[[一锅|一锅]]合成[[吖啶酮|吖啶酮]]衍生物 (3)。<ref>S Yoshida. ''Design, Synthesis and Characterization of Novel Heterocyclic Polymers'' (Thesis, McGill University, [[Montreal|Montreal]] ([[Canada|Canada]]))</ref><ref>[[Ioan_Tănăsescu|Ioan Tănăsescu]] ''Bull Soc Chim Fr'' 41 (1927) p528</ref><ref>[[Kurt_Lehmstedt|Kurt Lehmstedt]]  ''[[Chem._Ber.|Chem. Ber.]]'' 65 (1932) {{DOI|10.1002/cber.19320650531}}
 834</ref><ref>[[Kurt_Lehmstedt|Kurt Lehmstedt]] ''DE581328'' ([[patent|patent]])</ref><ref>I Silberg. ''Rev Roum Chim'' 10 (1965) 1035</ref>

